idi katha kaadu ( english : this is n't a story ) is a 1979 indian telugu language drama film directed by k. balachander starring kamal haasan , jayasudha , sarath babu , chiranjeevi , saritha , and ramaprabha . it is a remake of balachander 's earlier tamil hit &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( 1977 ) . jayasudha reprised the role of sujatha in the original . kamal haasan starred in the same role in both languages . this film also had chiranjeevi as the villainous husband of jayasudha ( rajinikanth starred as the husband in tamil ) . the film was shot in black and white .